aors.module.agentControl.gui.interaction
Interface Sender

All Superinterfaces:
InteractiveComponent
public interface Sender
extends InteractiveComponent

Interface that represents a gui component that acts as a send. A sender is a gui components that can sends its value when an user interaction is performed.
